flowchart LR
    Sess[session activity]
    Mem["context/memory/<br/>date.md session blocks"]
    Learn["context/learnings.md<br/>per-skill journal"]
    Prof["research-profile.md<br/>Activity Log"]

    Sess -->|incremental writes| Mem
    Sess -->|after deliverable| Feed{"user<br/>feedback?"}
    Feed -->|yes| Learn
    Sess -->|at wrap-up| Evolve[profile-evolve.py]
    Evolve --> Prof
    Evolve --> KeyProp{"recurring topics<br/>across sessions?"}
    KeyProp -->|yes| PropKey["propose new keywords<br/>user approves"]
    PropKey --> Prof

    Mem -->|scanned at wrap-up| Detect{"recurring manual<br/>workflow 3x+?"}
    Detect -->|yes| Proposal["propose skillification<br/>via meta-skill-creator"]
    Learn -->|next session start| Heartbeat["heartbeat loads<br/>last 5-10 entries"]

    Proposal -->|user approves| Build[scaffold new skill]
    Build --> Catalog[Skills Pack grows]

    style Mem fill:#fff3e0
    style Learn fill:#fff3e0
    style Prof fill:#fff3e0
    style Proposal fill:#ffe0e0
    style Build fill:#e8f5e9
